text: hey there good evening:blush:
Very good evening! How can I serve you today? :slightly_smiling_face:
I am looking for some restaurants for dinner.
For dinner I would suggest you to have a look at these.
The first and 5th ones look good. Can you specify the cuisines they serve?
They serve Indian, Italian, French, Spanish and Chinese. But they are highly recommended for Indian and chinese. :slightly_smiling_face:
Does the 1st image is served better in the previous first and fifth restaurants?
Yes the 1st one is served both in first and fifth restaurants. :wink:
Can you show the ambience of the 1st image?
Look at these images of ambiance from the 1st restaurant.
This is spacious :blush:, can you show the parking facility as well?
Yes, please. Here is the parking facility.
Great this is really nice:heart_eyes:. Can you show the menu for the 1st image?
Please Have a look at the menu card.!! :wink:
Whats the best in the starters they serve?
The best they serve in starters are :wink:
It seems fine, but do they only serve non-veg?
No, they also serve vegetarian starters also! The first image is vegetarian :slightly_smiling_face:
Can you show more varieties of the 1st image but less oily ones?
Have a look at these vegetarian starters :wink:
The 1st and 4th looks really yummy.:yum::yum: Can you please suggest some less spicy starters in non-veg?
Oh, that's nice. Yup let me get you that.
The 1st one looks really spicy:frowning: I need some less spicy for the kids similar to the 1st one.
Oh!! I am so sorry about that. Please consider these.
This seems quite better:blush: also can you suggest some desserts for the kids?
Yup! I guess kids will love ice creams and donuts  :slightly_smiling_face:
Its only chocolate:face_with_raised_eyebrow: Do you have in other flavours of the 2nd type and 4th?
Yup. I have got you the other flavours in 2nd and 4th variety. :stuck_out_tongue:
The 1st one looks delicious:heart_eyes:.
Do need any other information? :slightly_smiling_face:
Yes please I would like to know the timings of the restaurant?
The timings for the restaurant is 12:30 pm to 10:30 pm.
That's great, and also the average price per person.
The price per person is 300/- Rs only. :smile:
Great thanks for the information:smiley:
You are always welcome!!! :smile:
